00:21:37.440 --> 00:21:40.351 line:20%
'Sai meneleponku berkali-kali'

00:21:40.520 --> 00:21:42.360 line:20%
'setelah mengetahui
tentang misiku.'

00:21:42.720 --> 00:21:46.452 line:20%
'Jadi, kupikir Sai
sudah memaafkanku.'

00:21:46.720 --> 00:21:49.280 line:20%
'Saya harap Anda belum
